OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773958308
OL,3,CWorld's longest coastal path
OL,4,Cstretching 2,700 miles around England
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FThe world's longest managed coastal
OL,8,Fwalking route, which will stretch
OL,9,F2,700 miles around the English coast,
OL,10,Fopens on Thursday.
OL,12,FThe King Charles III England Coast
OL,13,FPath, which has been nearly two
OL,14,Fdecades in the making, snakes the
OL,15,Flength of England, is set to be
OL,16,Fcompleted in the near future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773958308
OL,3,CWorld's longest coastal path
OL,4,Cstretching 2,700 miles around England
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FThe coastal path will be the longest
OL,8,Fmanaged coastal walking route in the
OL,9,Fworld, with officials behind the
OL,10,Fscheme estimating the path would take
OL,11,Fa year to walk ` with weekends off.
OL,13,FWhy has this been created?
OL,15,FNatural England has been working on
OL,16,Fthe development of what is now known
OL,17,Fas the King Charles III England
OL,18,FCoastal Path, since plans for a
OL,19,Fnational coastal route around the
OL,20,Fwhole of England were first legislated
OL,21,Ffor in 2009.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773958308
OL,3,CWorld's longest coastal path
OL,4,Cstretching 2,700 miles around England
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FThe coastal route, which will be a
OL,8,Fnational trail, has extended legal
OL,9,Faccess from about two-thirds of the
OL,10,Fcoast of England to the entire open
OL,11,Fcoast, creating about 1,000 miles of
OL,12,Fnew legal access.
OL,14,FNatural England's programme manager
OL,15,Ffor the coast path, Neil Constable
OL,16,Fsaid: "The whole point of this will be
OL,17,Fthat you can basically hit the coast
OL,18,Fanywhere and turn right or left, and
OL,19,Fthere should be assigned route to
OL,20,Ffollow."
OL,26,@xD@GOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773958308
OL,3,CWorld's longest coastal path
OL,4,Cstretching 2,700 miles around England
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FHe said the #28 million scheme had had
OL,8,Fto deal with "curveballs" such as
OL,9,Fnature conservation rulings, Covid,
OL,10,Fand the increase in material costs
OL,11,Fafter the invasion of Ukraine.
OL,13,FBut he added: "Give it 20 years, and
OL,14,Fit will take on its own identity, its
OL,15,Fown focus, things will come out of it
OL,16,F` there will be a lot of books written
OL,17,Fabout it, and so on."
OL,19,FWhat will I see on the route - and how
OL,20,Fchallenging will it be?
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@YO]uD@OOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
