PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773958308
OL,3,CWorld's longest coastal path
OL,4,Cstretching 2,700 miles around England
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FFrom beachside castles in the North
OL,8,FEast, to the rolling Seven Sisters
OL,9,Fchalk cliffs and Dorset's Jurassic
OL,10,FCoast, there is plenty to see no
OL,11,Fmatter which part of the coastline you
OL,12,Fpick.
OL,14,FThe route, which was renamed the King
OL,15,FCharles III England Coast Path to mark
OL,16,Fthe King's coronation and his
OL,17,Fchampioning of the natural world,
OL,18,Fincorporates and has improved parts of
OL,19,Fexisting national trails such as the
OL,20,FSouth West and Norfolk coast paths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773958308
OL,3,CWorld's longest coastal path
OL,4,Cstretching 2,700 miles around England
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FIn some areas, such as seal pupping
OL,8,Fsites in the east of England or areas
OL,9,Fof Somerset with wintering birds on
OL,10,Fwater courses, there will be
OL,11,Frestrictions such as seasonal changes
OL,12,Fto the route or dogs-on-leads
OL,13,Frequirements to protect nature.
OL,15,FThe team have opted for gates or open
OL,16,Fgaps rather than stiles, and in places
OL,17,Fhas made improvements to the route.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
