PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773958308
OL,3,CWorld's longest coastal path
OL,4,Cstretching 2,700 miles around England
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FMr Constable, pointed to one case in
OL,8,FFalmouth, Cornwall, where a very muddy
OL,9,Fsection of track was surfaced,
OL,10,Fallowing a local woman with cerebral
OL,11,Fpalsy to access the path for the first
OL,12,Ftime.
OL,14,FDoes this mean I can now walk all the
OL,15,Fway around Britain?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
