PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773958308
OL,3,CWorld's longest coastal path
OL,4,Cstretching 2,700 miles around England
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FAll of the proposals for the 2,700
OL,8,Fmile route have been published and
OL,9,Fsubmitted to government, with the
OL,10,FNatural England team expecting to have
OL,11,Fcompleted 90% of infrastructure work
OL,12,Fby the summer ` although the vast
OL,13,Fmajority of the path is already
OL,14,Fwalkable as most is natural surface.
OL,16,FEngland's new section of the coastal
OL,17,Fpath joins up with the Wales Coast
OL,18,FPath - an 870-mile route encircling
OL,19,Fthe Welsh coastline which was
OL,20,Fcompleted in 2012.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
