OL,3,CWorld's longest coastal path
OL,4,Cstretching 2,700 miles around England
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FScotland's "right to roam" law already
OL,8,Fgives walkers access to its coastline
OL,9,Fwhich measures around 5,500 miles long.
